
Overview of adv especially

The adv especially has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                      
1. (66) particularly, peculiarly, especially, specially -- (to a distinctly greater extent or degree than is common; "he was particularly fussy about spelling"; "a particularly gruesome attack"; "under peculiarly tragic circumstances"; "an especially (or specially) cautious approach to the danger")
2. specially, especially -- (in a special manner; "a specially arranged dinner")
